CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 30, 1954, pg. 1, reads: "Eaten by Flames - The interior of one of the homes, gutted by fire in 1500 block of North Murtland Street, last Saturday, is shown. Only the charred walls remain.  With great speed  the fire spread from the basement of 1506 1/2 North Murtland Street and spread to the flat roof. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Interior hallway of burned row house, with dark leaf patterned sofa in room on left, 1500 block North Murtland Street, Homewood
